        <item>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Religious Freedom International Reciprocity Enhancement Act or the Religious FIRE Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits a foreign national of a country that limits the free exercise of religion in that country from making any expenditure in the United States promoting a religion.</p> <p>An asset consisting of such an expenditure or the proceeds of such an expenditure is subject to U.S. forfeiture.</p>]]></text>
